{
  "stem": "24137.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was a great, great [YIDDISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, he was a very righteous man because he hid a lot of people in his house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and he helped so many people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember whoever came, he took them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He did never, ever say, I have no room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or I have no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I think why I think it was a long time that I was there is because he had sisters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And these sisters took it upon themselves to teach us little children how to tell time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was the hardest thing, because it, you know, it was by, by numbers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It wasn't these digital clocks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was the big event, that we had to learn how to tell time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember I used to always hide in the bathroom, not to have to all the time learn this time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I-- finally, when I left Wieliczka, I knew how to tell time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it must have been a long time that I was there, but also because a lot of things happened there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A lot of people came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A lot of people went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so it seemed like maybe it was six months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one night when we were out in the back, in the backyard, in the garden, the neighbors ran to the Gestapo and told them that my uncle is hiding Jews in his house.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Gestapo came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they kicked in the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was evening, so we all were out of the, of the basement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were up in the living room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they rounded everybody up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a outhouse in this garden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I took the two little girls and me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
